<section class="section" aria-labelledby="roadmap-sections-title">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <div>
      <h2 id="roadmap-sections-title">Current roadmap</h2>
      <p class="section-meta">Last updated: May 20, 2026</p>
    </div>
    <p>Priorities may change as the app evolves.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="roadmap-grid">
    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Shipped recently</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-shipped">Shipped</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Client pricing</strong> &mdash; Turn calculated print costs into a client-ready price with markup, setup fees, rounding, and currency formatting. Cost and price stay separate so makers can see both what a print costs and what they should charge.</li>
        <li>Materials management improvements &mdash; Search and filter your material library, track stock levels, and import materials from CSV.</li>
        <li>New Help page with FAQs and support links to help you get started faster.</li>
        <li>Refined settings layout that makes key options easier to find.</li>
        <li>Risk calculation fixes for more accurate cost estimates.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>In Progress</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-in-progress">In Progress</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Batch costing</strong> &mdash; Estimate the cost and final price for batches that include multiple copies, multiple models, or a mix of both. Batch costing will help makers price repeat orders and multi-part jobs more accurately by accounting for quantity, shared setup time, and per-item costs.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Planned</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-planned">Planned</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Shareable quotes</strong> &mdash; Build on client pricing with a cleaner quote-style view that can be shared with customers.</li>
        <li>Backup and restore with JSON files</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Exploring</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-exploring">Exploring</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li>CSV export for material lists</li>
        <li>More client-facing pricing outputs</li>
        <li><strong>Improved electricity estimates</strong> &mdash; Get more accurate electricity cost estimates by adding an optional average print power to printer profiles. Printers often use much less power while actively printing than their rated maximum. This lets you set a realistic average wattage while keeping the existing maximum as a fallback.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

